This hotel has quickly become my preferred Hotel when I visit Vancouver, knocking Sutton Place, The Fairmont Hotel Vancouver and Hyatt out of my top preferred Hotels in the area.	We left two days earlier than scheduled and ended up spending our last two days at our favorite hotel, Bellevue Club in Bellevue, WA.	I travelled to Vancouver on business for many years and this hotel was my favorite.	The bathroom was my favorite - oversized tub and gorgeous tile.	So I went to the amazing Sara Bareilles concert in Vancouver and was fortunate to find this hotel on my iPhone via Google Maps!